title: NFL ATL: Go Get My Lunch -- Draft Edition
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Go Get My Lunch -- Draft Edition
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- makes some bold predictions about the 2014 NFL Draft and backs them up by putting some sandwiches on the line.  Elsewhere, the gang runs through the latest headlines around the league and talks through the biggest storylines ahead of next week’s big show at Radio City Music Hall.
